request.description:
Returns all voices grouped by engine and category.

Example response:
```json
{
  "qwen": {
    "built_in":  ["Aiden", "Chelsie", "Ryan", ...],
    "cloneable": ["my_voice.wav"]
  },
  "kokoro": {
    "en-us": ["af_heart", "af_bella", ...],
    "en-gb": ["bf_emma", ...],
    "ja":    ["jf_alpha", ...],
    "zh":    ["zf_xiaobei", ...]
  },
  "piper": {
    "en_US": ["en_US-lessac-medium"],
    "en_GB": ["en_GB-alba-medium"]
  }
}
```

Cloneable voice files and Piper voices are read from disk at request time — no restart needed.
